is a life about to start<br />\nWhen tomorrow comes!<br />\n<br />\nWill you join in our crusade?<br />\nWho will be strong and stand with me?<br />\nSomewhere beyond the barricade<br />\nIs there a world you long to see?<br />\n<br />\nThen join in the fight<br />\nThat will give you the right to be free!<br />\n<br />\nDo you hear the people sing?<br />\nSinging the songs of angry men?<br />\nIt is the music of the people<br />\n<br />\nWho will not be slaves again!<br />\nWhen the beating of your heart<br />\nEchoes the beating of the drums<br />\nThere is a life about to start<br />\nWhen tomorrow comes!<br />\n<br />\nWill you give all you can give<br />\nSo that our banner may advance<br />\nSome will fall and some will live<br />\nWill you stand up and take your chance?<br />\nThe blood of the martyrs<br />\nWill water the meadows of France!<br />\n<br />\nDo you hear the people sing?<br />\nSinging the songs of angry men?<br />\nIt is the music of the people<br />\nWho will not be slaves again!<br />\nWhen the beating of your heart<br />\nEchoes the beating of the drums<br />\nThere is a life about to start<br />\nWhen tomorrow comes"},{"pid":"582c8410c946c602b236553cf95af227879b0612","tid":1355950,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:44:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"36cab5299332d4784eb679caa5244db3bb0a18c8","tid":1355950,"uid":167289,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"首先要練吓點唱<br />\n首歌唔易唱<br />\n睇死到時唱到亂七八糟個個唔同 Beat"},{"pid":"5afb5b9bfdecd04b29e4fd36c7e9923ed4bfeda4","tid":1355950,"uid":240224,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"36cab5299332d4784eb679caa5244db3bb0a18c8","tid":1355950,"uid":167289,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:45:37.000Z","msg":"首先要練吓點唱<br />\n首歌唔易唱<br />\n睇死到時唱到亂七八糟個個唔同 Beat"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"有無得帶個大喇叭去播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cla